<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Policy Update Notice</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div>
      <div>
        <h1>Policy Update Notice</h1>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p>Hello User,</p>

        <p>
          We're writing to inform you that we have updated our policies. It's
          important that you review these changes as they may affect how you use
          our services.
        </p>

        <div>
          <div>Policy Updated</div>
          <div><%= title %></div>
          <div>Updated on <%= updateDate %></div>
        </div>

        <div>
          <a href="<%= policyPage %>" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
            View Updated <%=title%>
          </a>
        </div>

        <div>
          <div>ðŸ“¢ Important Information</div>
          <p>
            By continuing to use our services after <%= updateDate %>, you agree
            to be bound by the updated policy. Please take a few minutes to
            review the changes.
          </p>
        </div>

        <p>
          If you have any questions about these changes or need clarification,
          please don't hesitate to contact our support team.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <p>
          This is an important policy notification. Please review the updated
          terms.
        </p>
        <p>Need help? Contact our support team for assistance.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
